  <official_title>A 12 Week, Multi-center, Randomized, Open Label Study, eValuating the Efficacy and Safety of Treatment Regimens That Include ONbrez (Indacaterol) in Patients With Moderate to Severe COPD (MOVE-ON Study)</official_title>
